} \\geq 100$. Our numerical technique and simulations revealed also a\ngood qualitative agreement with the magneto optical imaging observations that\nwere questioning the CST validness, proving therefore that the reported\nphenomena for self-field SC-SFM heterostructures can be understood without\nincluding the ansatz of overcritical currents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Sep 2021 17:05:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 2021 15:52:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-22"}
