ards the faint\nend of the class are, however, not reproduced. This motivates a quantification\nof the systematic uncertainties in the modeling procedure and the influence of\nthe $^{56}$Ni-rich bound remnant. While the pure deflagration scenario remains\na favorable explanation for bright and intermediate luminosity SNe~Iax, the\npossibility that SNe~Iax do not consist of a single explosion scenario needs to\nbe considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 08:27:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2021 08:12:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
