 observable and produce catalogs of the gamma-ray polarization of GRBs.\nHere we will present an overview of the POLAR mission and all its scientific\nmeasurement results. Additionally, we will present an overview of the future\nPOLAR-2 mission, and how it will answer some of the questions raised by the\nPOLAR results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 10:18:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
