 and polarization results of the\nCrab pulsar with POLAR. Finally, the inferred ability of pulsar detection with\nPOLAR-2 (the successor of POLAR) will also be discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 15:18:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
